AT SELECTION-SCREEN OUTPUT.

  LOOP AT SCREEN.

    "Planner Group (SO_VAGRP)
    IF screen-name CP 'SO_VAGRP-*'.
      screen-value_help = 'X'.
      MODIFY SCREEN.
    ENDIF.

    "Header Work Center (SO_ARBH)
    IF screen-name CP 'SO_ARBH-*'.
      screen-value_help = 'X'.
      MODIFY SCREEN.
    ENDIF.

    "Operation Work Center (SO_ARBPO)
    IF screen-name CP 'SO_ARBPO-*'.
      screen-value_help = 'X'.
      MODIFY SCREEN.
    ENDIF.

  ENDLOOP.